public enum AdjustApplyType
extends java.lang.Enum<AdjustApplyType>
implements org.eclipse.emf.common.util.Enumerator

A representation of the literals of the enumeration 'Adjust Apply Type', and utility methods for working with them. enum for apply adjustment. DuringIteration - apply the adjustment as soon as mismatch at a bus is small; PostIteration - apply the adjustment after the whole network is near coveragance.
